.TH UTILITYKIT 1 "July 2026" "UtilityKit v5.10.6" "UtilityKit Tools"
.SH NAME
utility-pdf_toolkit \- Merge, split, extract text, compress, rotate, and inspect PDFs.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B utility pdf_toolkit
[\fIoptions\fP]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Merge, split, extract text, compress, rotate, and inspect PDFs.
.SH DEPENDENCIES
.PP
Tool   |   Package   |   Purpose
\fCqpdf\fP   |   \fCqpdf\fP   |   Core operations (recommended)
\fCpdftotext\fP   |   \fCpoppler-utils\fP   |   Text extraction
\fCgs\fP   |   \fCghostscript\fP   |   Compression
\fCpdfinfo\fP   |   \fCpoppler-utils\fP   |   Metadata
.PP
.SH USAGE
.PP
.EX
pdf info document.pdf
pdf count document.pdf
pdf merge a.pdf b.pdf --output merged.pdf
pdf split document.pdf --output ./pages/
pdf text document.pdf
pdf compress document.pdf --output compressed.pdf
pdf rotate document.pdf 90
.EE
.PP
.SH OPTIONS
.PP
Flag   |   Meaning
\fC--output FILE\fP   |   Output path
\fC--pages RANGE\fP   |   Page range (e.g. 1-3,5)
\fC--json\fP   |   Machine-readable output
